{"tid":2263772,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"衝出香港丨《理大圍城》入圍阿姆斯特丹國際紀錄片影展爭獎 11月歐洲首映","createTime":"2020-10-30T06:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T07:18:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d15f5b9b0c34426251e0ea6d3f422c3af558bd9d","tid":2263772,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:42:50.000Z","msg":"紀錄片《理大圍城》及《佔領立法會》上月底舉行放映會，疑遭電檢處多方面打壓。事實上反對聲音禁不住，《佔》已先入圍下月舉行的台灣金馬獎最佳紀錄片獎。發行商影意志昨日在網上公告，《理大》已入圍荷蘭阿姆斯特丹國際紀錄片電影節 (IDFA)競賽部份爭獎，《佔領》亦入圍非競賽部份。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201030/JC33753O2ZBZPEHIBWI7QSIJIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201030%2FJC33753O2ZBZPEHIBWI7QSIJIU%2F&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=0280ef8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201030%2FJC33753O2ZBZPEHIBWI7QSIJIU%2F&h=60b26de4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201030/JC33753O2ZBZPEHIBWI7QSIJIU/</a>"},{"pid":"8a6f466e49a7fe8aa6c2da6a7c8604fc959dfd8d","tid":2263772,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"係，點先睇到"},{"pid":"c7d8eb9295e0667907aa811ecf135d95b4c1ec8a","tid":2263772,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"支那：嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}